{"tid":2386300,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳維景灣畔3房套微減12萬元 1068萬元沽","createTime":"2021-01-29T13:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T03:33:32.000Z","uid":166360,"like":5,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d9748b84b3c5642ea99d167e34b59d8d98725bf3","tid":2386300,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"將軍澳維景灣畔3房套微減12萬元 1068萬元沽<br />\n21:00 2021/01/29<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......將軍澳維景灣畔1期6座中低層C室單位的二手成交個案，實用面積約664平方呎，建築面積約902平方呎，採三房套間隔，外望可享清幽山景。單位於上年12月初開始放售，業主原叫價1,080萬元，日前終以1,068萬元成功易手，減價12萬元或1%，折合實用面積呎價約16,084元......<br />\n<br />\n......持貨至今21年，現轉手帳面獲利約765.9萬元，物業升值約2.5倍......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2866004/%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E7%B6%AD%E6%99%AF%E7%81%A3%E7%95%943%E6%88%BF%E5%A5%97%E5%BE%AE%E6%B8%9B12%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%201068%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%B2%BD?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2866004%2F%25E5%25B0%2587%25E8%25BB%258D%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%2599%25AF%25E7%2581%25A3%25E7%2595%25943%25E6%2588%25BF%25E5%25A5%2597%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E6%25B8%259B12%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25201068%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%25B2%25BD%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=mGfgamXUORjeED7mKz2VH0bB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=640b6b60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2866004/%E5%B0%87%E8%BB%8D%E6%BE%B3%E7%B6%AD%E6%99%AF%E7%81%A3%E7%95%943%E6%88%BF%E5%A5%97%E5%BE%AE%E6%B8%9B12%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%201068%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%B2%BD?mtc=60037</a>"},{"pid":"118a2d7c6b427f5d949009bd2f12b19f09bfd704","tid":2386300,"uid":73269,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T15:43:17.000Z","msg":"好低買<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ab5ba75433f1fd261d02e1ce711f723d0ab755","tid":2386300,"uid":76471,"like":2,"dislike":